snippet.title: Assault On Metaltron Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready to play as defense Golem? Dance, build and protect your home planet Metaltron from invaders.

Available on Steam and Nintendo Switch.

Music by Kubbi ('Seahorse Dreams')
